		<pb n="1"/>
			<p rend="align(right)"><placeName>Atlanta</placeName> <date><sic>february</sic> 20 1852</date></p>
			<p><addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(2)">Dr Sir</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">I hope you arrived home safe<lb/> and well&#44; my family is well thank god. The object<lb/> of this is to ask you to decide a <sic>bett</sic> which was made<lb/> between <persName>Mr Mayer</persName> &#38; myself. I <sic>bett</sic> on the authority<lb/> of your almanac attached to the Occident of<lb/> last <date>August</date>&#44; that <date>Purim</date> falls on the <date>11th of March</date><lb/> he says on the <date>5th of March</date>&#44; how is it&#63; please let<lb/> me know by return mail. All friends here<lb/> send their best respects</p>
          <p rend="indent(3)">Yours truly</p>
          <p rend="indent(4)"><persName role="author">A J Brady</persName></p>
		<pb n="2"/>
			<p><addressee>Rev. Isaac Leeser</addressee></p>
          <p rend="indent(1)"><placeName>Philadelphia</placeName></p>
          
